<!DOCTYPE match SYSTEM "match.dtd">
<match>
	<company side="greenfor">
		<platoon>
			<slot shortcode="PTL"/>
			<slot shortcode="PTS"/>
			<slot shortcode="PTM"/>
			<slot shortcode="R"/>
			<squad callsign="Reaper" radio-frequency="85.5">
				<slot shortcode="SQL" description="squad leader"/>
				<slot shortcode="SQM" description="squad medic"/>
				<fireteam>
					<slot shortcode="FTL" description="fireteam lead"><user uid="5"/></slot>
					<slot shortcode="GR" description="fireteam lead"><user uid="6"/></slot>
					<slot shortcode="R"/>
					<slot shortcode="AR" description="automatic rifleman"/>
				</fireteam>
				<fireteam>
					<slot shortcode="FTL" description="fireteam lead"><user uid="1"/></slot>
					<slot shortcode="GR" description="fireteam lead"><user uid="2"/></slot>
					<slot shortcode="R"/>
					<slot shortcode="AR" description="automatic rifleman"><reservation>Adler</reservation></slot>
				</fireteam>
			</squad>
			<squad callsign="Hunter">
				<slot shortcode="PIL" description="pilot">
					<reservation>TF47</reservation>
				</slot>
			</squad>
		</platoon>
		<platoon callsign="bumper"/>
	</company>
</match>
